# Event-driven Dual DB (Oracle + Postgres) with Kafka

## Start infrastructure
docker compose up -d

## Run services (3 terminals)
cd work-order-service && mvn spring-boot:run
cd reporting-service && mvn spring-boot:run
cd notification-service && mvn spring-boot:run

## Test
curl -X POST http://localhost:8081/api/work-orders \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"site":"DFW","assetType":"AHU","assetId":"AHU-12","priority":"HIGH","description":"Low SAT"}'

## Verify Postgres reporting table
docker exec -it postgres psql -U reporting_user -d reporting -c "select * from work_order_report;"